## Interface: 30300
## Title: COA State Plates - Aggro
## Notes: The "I care about aggro" surface for COA State Plates: loading this addon adds a minimal native options page (Interface > AddOns) that turns on the core's native threat-border steering and aggro-highlight control. All machinery lives in the core addon (baseline off); this addon is only the declaration of interest + its config page. Disable this addon and the core returns to baseline.
## Author: Battlewrath
## Version: 1.0.0
## Dependencies: COA_GuardianPlates

